# === DOMAIN LOCK: Canonical domain enforcement ===
# All traffic MUST resolve to https://www.visitarealdelmonte.online
# Redirect apex domain to www
https://visitarealdelmonte.online/* https://www.visitarealdelmonte.online/:splat 301
# Block non-canonical deployment domains (vercel.app, cloudflare pages, lovable previews)
# These must be configured as Page Rules in Cloudflare Dashboard:
#   - visitarealdelmonte.online/* → https://www.visitarealdelmonte.online/* (301)
#   - *.vercel.app/* → return 404
#   - *.pages.dev/* → return 404
#
# SPA fallback for client-side routing on Cloudflare Pages.
/*    /index.html   200
